Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:52.48,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,We might all be executed, not just Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:54.88,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,What she did would warrant that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.39,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.15,Flashback_Italics,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,There's just one way to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:05.90,Flashback,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Only the Demon King has the \Nauthority to overturn a law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:10.37,Flashback,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If the Demon King awakens before \Nthe execution is carried out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.09,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I got us a hot water pot and a tea set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.80,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.47,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,The guards look scary, \Nbut they were very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sister, you were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There's a garden where they grow \Na bunch of different plants!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:33.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Excellent! Now if I can \Njust get some herbs—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.05,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'll go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.86,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But if someone sees you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:38.74,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,No need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.09,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I can also take this form!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What in all hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.21,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,U-Um, Lady Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.21,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Squeeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.51,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This isn't so bad every now \Nand then, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:53.30,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.31,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Flap, flap, flap...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.87,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Flap, flap, flap...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:55.87,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:56.77,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Plink. Plonk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:57.63,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Plop. Plop. Plop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.74,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:08.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,An analeptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's just incredibly bitter \Nand hard-hitting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:16.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But it's so bitter, I'm sure \Nit'll awaken the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:19.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Vania?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:24.48,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Lady Beelzebub ordered me \Nto bring this to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:29.96,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,The Demon King rests in this first-aid room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But the question is how to get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.58,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Lady Beelzebub has a plan for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.22,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.02,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is like some kind of lame comedy skit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:47.35,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Rumble, rumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Take this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:48.93,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I-I am serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.28,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Flail, flail, flail...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:51.69,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,The current crisis has the \Nwhole castle in a panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.74,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I'm sure no one's paid attention \Nto the identity of the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Really, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.69,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I will guide you through \Nthe rest personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:00.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.13,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.62,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.58,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.54,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Zoom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If we're found out, \Nwon't you get caught, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:16.91,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:22.55,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I don't even fully understand how this \Nturned into such a serious matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:25.95,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,But Lady Beelzebub gave me \Norders, so I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.68,Main,Demon A,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.92,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I am Vania, a servant of Lady Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.60,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I've brought the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.87,Main,Demon B,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:40.43,Main,Demon B,0,0,0,,I have not received any reports \Nof Beelzebub summoning anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:43.02,Main,Demon B,0,0,0,,I already know the doctor's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.54,Main,Demon B,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:49.37,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,H-H-H-Her name is... A-Azu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.31,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Pero... Poro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.37,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,We're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.55,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.43,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're ignoring us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.68,Main,Demon A,0,0,0,,Something doesn't smell right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:01.40,Main,Demon A,0,0,0,,And what's with those horns? \NDid you just stick them on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.80,Main,Demon A,0,0,0,,Let me check for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.95,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.16,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I am Azusa, the Witch of the Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I will awaken the Demon King right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.55,Main,Demon A,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.13,Main,Demon B,0,0,0,,A friend of the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:15.86,Main,Demon C,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.41,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But for the sake of Halkara \Nand the rest of my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.71,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I can't just sit here and let you take me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.32,Main,Demon A,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.94,Main,Demon B,0,0,0,,I-In a mere instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.97,Main,Demon C,0,0,0,,Just what is this human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:39.27,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let me get to the Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.22,Main,Demon A,0,0,0,,Defend to the last!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.75,Main,Demon B,0,0,0,,You have permission to use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.49,Main,Demon C,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:06:00.52,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I never imagined it would turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.69,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess I went a little too far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:08.19,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,When you mean business, you could \Nflatten an entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.01,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Y-You were awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.17,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I sensed that a ruffian was approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.01,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,so I woke up instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.05,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bwiiing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're a Demon King, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.86,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,What were you trying to get me to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:41.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I-It's just an analeptic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I was only trying to wake you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.54,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,It looks a lot like poison to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:48.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It only {\i1}looks{\i0} like poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:52.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you drink it, you'll be like, \N"Augh, gross! But I want another!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.42,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Very well, Witch of the Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.25,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,If you wish to prove your innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:00.41,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,then face me, Provat Pecora Allières,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.68,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,in a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:10.50,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,If what you've said is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:15.20,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,then even if you win, \Nyou won't try to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I mean, I get the idea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:22.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That would only work if I won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.66,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,If you lose, then it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:29.48,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Only the fact that the Demon King \Ndefeated an assassin will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess that means I have no choice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.62,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Now, Witch of the Highlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.37,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I will judge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.62,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,just how powerful you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.63,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Losing is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.95,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,All of our lives depend on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.61,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't believe she evaded that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.37,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}am{\i0} level 99.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.49,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Why don't you try attacking me a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.38,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You'd better not drag your feet too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.58,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Remember, that elf's life is on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.43,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,That wasn't a very wise taunt, Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.81,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,When it comes to protecting my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll show no hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:54.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'd say we're done here, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.71,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I only lost my balance, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But I've already destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.13,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You can always train your body more,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.77,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but you can only strengthen \Na weapon so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Am I wrong, Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:23.14,Eyecatch,Title,0,0,0,,I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes\N{\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years {\c&H313536&}and\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I do believe I've won, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Are you going to do as I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.45,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I want you to spare Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,She doesn't mean any harm. \NShe's just a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Uh... Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.42,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,All right, Dear Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.36,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What? Dear Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.70,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I will obey your every order, Dear Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.76,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:10:00.27,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,For some time, I've wanted to live my life \Nin reverence for one stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.93,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I thought you would be the \Nperfect choice for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.04,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,so I took the liberty of testing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:06.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:10.82,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'd like to respect and adore you for \Nthe rest of my life, Dear Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um... I'm honored, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:14.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but before any of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:18.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,could you please guarantee \Nthe safety of Halkara and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.23,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Please don't speak so politely to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.72,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Say it like you're giving me an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.24,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Oh, and with your hand on my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:27.88,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Provat—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.76,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Please, call me Pecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:32.74,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Pecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.63,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,D-Dear Sister, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:46.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Pecora, you are to set Halkara free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Simple enough, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:57.33,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,It has been proven that Halkara did \Nnot knock me out intentionally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.44,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,She is to be set free!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.47,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,And treat all of Azusa's \Nfamily with utmost care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.70,Main,Demons,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.31,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it all worked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.50,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Slither, slither, slither...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.50,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,And our lives are saved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.80,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Sorry, but would you mind humoring her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.67,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Gulp, gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.76,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I never dreamed I'd get to enjoy \Ntea like this with my dear sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.49,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to have an older sister now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:35.52,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I had grown tired of making people serve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:39.84,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Everyone automatically denigrates \Nthemselves before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.07,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, you {\i1}are{\i0} the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:46.31,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,When you slammed me against the \Nwall, my heart skipped a beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:50.02,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,A woman with such a dignified \Nexpression as she gives me orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.53,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,My heart was simply pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.36,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Drool...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:54.51,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:56.64,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Beelzebub was a candidate \Nto be my older sister, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.50,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,but she wouldn't scold me or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,She seems like she'd be \Na better fit than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.36,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:07.72,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,If there's ever anything the demons \Ncan help you with, just ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:10.84,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'll do everything in my \Npower for my dear sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:15.44,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Um, Dear Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.82,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,There's one favor I'd like to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:20.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Uh... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:23.81,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Would you please give \Nme a kiss on the cheek?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.25,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.41,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,There's a scene in my favorite book
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:30.67,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,where the older sister \Nkisses her younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.13,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I just love that so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:35.49,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,and I really want to experience it myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.48,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,And look, there's no one else around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.81,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec! A kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:44.91,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,People kiss members of their \Nown families, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.54,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,It's just an extension of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.15,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm not kissing you! \NI'll give you a hug, at most!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.29,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You should!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.03,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Especially for your little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.22,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,O-Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But only on your cheek, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.02,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Dear Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.78,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I was genuinely scared, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.94,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,That was a close one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.16,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Dangerously close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes closed, Pecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.91,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Please try to be a bit more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:24.79,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I was so worried abo—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master and the Demon King \Nare a c-c-c-c-coupl—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:36.55,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master... you're the type who \Nfalls in love with women?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.97,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,W-Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.31,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,You have my support!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's not like that! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:46.56,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You've intruded upon my precious \Ntime with my dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:49.61,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Have you no tact whatsoever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.24,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.44,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.49,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let her off the hook! I'll kiss you, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.13,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,No need anymore. The mood's already ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:03.06,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,A kiss between sisters is a sacred \Nritual to deepen their bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.56,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of merely \Ntouching with the lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.23,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sounds complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:11.21,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama, I don't think you've ever kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.06,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Falfa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:14.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.40,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yay! Mama gave me a kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.59,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.18,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I want one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.28,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You didn't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.30,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I... did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:36.59,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.24,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I'll give you one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.72,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.47,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Mama... Smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.16,Main,Three,0,0,0,,Je t'aime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,The rest of you get hugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:47.89,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pout...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:48.69,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Squeeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:49.80,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pat, pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.05,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.51,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Then, I want one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:59.14,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I think I might not be \Nvery fond of this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.53,Main - Top,Halkara,0,0,0,,If I had to say, I don't \Nthink she's my type, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:05.23,Main - Top,Halkara,0,0,0,,Spoiled girls like her need a \Ntaste of how harsh the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.53,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot. Laika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.95,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,There'll be a part of the ceremony \Ntomorrow that might surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:15.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow, there are so many people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:20.38,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Even I was prepared to lose \Nmy head after all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.41,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.54,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'll be more careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:31.30,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for taking time from \Nyour busy schedules to attend today's ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:36.15,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'd like to get straight to the awarding \Nof the Demon Medals of Honor in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.92,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Next, the peace category.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.04,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Azusa, the Witch of the Highlands,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.61,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,who halted the long-standing conflict \Nbetween the Red Dragons and the Blue Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:52.45,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,and Laika the Red Dragon, \Nif you would both step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.73,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,What? Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:03.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So this was the surprise \Nyou hinted at yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:11.38,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'd like to call one more to the stage: \NFlatorte, representing the Blue Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.38,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:17.80,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Flatorte has brought the Blue Dragons \Ntogether to assure no further conflicts arise,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.77,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,which I believe is worthy of recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.22,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I-It's been a while, Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.27,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.42,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You really seem to like surprising peopl—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.89,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,And now for the awards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.15,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.07,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Toss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.65,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Catch! Catch! Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.75,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Haphazard much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:39.16,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,This should go even further to ensure \Npeace between the Dragon tribes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:43.44,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Surely there's no one who would \Nstart a fight now, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.44,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I-I understand clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:48.04,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,The Blue Dragons won't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.80,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,After being forced to say that \Non a stage this prestigious,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.76,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,there's no way she'll break that treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Pecora, you actually thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.14,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,The demons themselves are \Na highly multiracial clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:03.39,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,The Demon King has to be a symbol \Nof the harmony among them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.77,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.24,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I still have many things I need to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.82,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Oh, I came up with a bit of an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:17.58,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'd like you to demonstrate proof to my dear \Nsister that the Blue Dragons won't rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:21.51,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I know! You should stroke Flatorte's horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.07,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,N-Not my horns! Anything but my horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:28.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Do you hate having your \Nhorns touched that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:30.08,Main - Top,Pecora,0,0,0,,I was a bit concerned my own \Ncleansing wouldn't be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:31.25,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It's a custom unique to the Blue Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.92,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Letting someone touch your horns \Nmeans you submit to them completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.94,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Would you rather have \NLaika touch them, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:42.32,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,That would give the Red Dragons \Ntotal control over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, it's all for the sake of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.77,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Have it your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.02,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Blast it all! I don't even care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.48,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Honored ancestors...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.19,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I have been forced to submit to this witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.68,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for bringing \Nsuch shame upon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's being a bit dramatic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:16.47,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,This concludes the awarding ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:26.49,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,I, Fatla, will be your attendant \Nfor the return trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.77,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,I am the one you rode to the Demon Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh! Thanks for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.42,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,My younger sister, Vania, \Nwill be your transport now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.71,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Incidentally... how long \Nare you going to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:43.06,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Now that I have sworn submission \Nto the Witch of the Highlands,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.24,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I cannot leave my mistress's \Nside for even a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait, you're coming home with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.78,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:50.83,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.70,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Our house in the highlands \Ndoesn't need two dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.62,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Please order Flatorte to \Nreturn to her homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.40,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Our customs demand that I \Nkill myself if I leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.77,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I must protect my mistress, \Nwherever she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Their customs are hardcore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Pecora, you knew all this \Nwhen you made me touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.80,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That damn demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.95,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Everyone, I've brought some honey wa...ter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.58,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.71,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that shaking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:22.63,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,It was Vania. She must have recalled \Nsomething that made her laugh again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:25.84,Italics,Vania,0,0,0,,This is Vania, your driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.67,Italics,Vania,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.00,Italics,Vania,0,0,0,,I just remembered a joke
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.17,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,from a comedy I saw two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.00,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Flatorte...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:37.38,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,So long as I live, I will \Nprotect you, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.51,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Fatla, is it okay if I use the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:48.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey... Don't you think that custom about \Ntotal submission is kinda unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:55.19,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,We Blue Dragons swore lifelong submission \Nto a dragon knight who overpowered us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.94,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,To the strong go all spoils, \Nand the master's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.26,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,These are my tribe's values.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:05.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then if I ordered you to die, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:07.11,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,If you so ordered it, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.84,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,That is the pride of the Blue Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Flatorte, I have one order for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Once we reach the house in the highlands,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:22.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,you are to think for yourself and act of \Nyour own will, without awaiting my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:25.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Throw away all thoughts of \Nsubmission and live freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:28.98,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,But then... I wouldn't know how to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.77,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,My orders are absolute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.54,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So obey my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.76,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll give you all the advice you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you're wrong, I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But you have to live independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:44.84,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.90,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.84,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,That order is contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter. I'm your mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.33,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:01.66,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Before we return to the others, \Ncan I ask you to do one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:08.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Uh... So you just want me to \Npet your head and horns now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.59,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:18.19,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Ah... I belong to you, my mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:22.50,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,She spent all those years trying her \Nhardest to be the Blue Dragons' leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:21.64,Main - Top,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.06,Main - Top,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:25.75,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,She couldn't show any \Nweakness or rely on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:26.82,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:28.65,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.32,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,You're bothering Lady Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.10,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It's time for you to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:34.46,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.21,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Why did you have to butt in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:39.57,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,You were doing something weird, \Nso I stopped you! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:42.07,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You Red Dragons are always \Ndoing such silly things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.37,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "weird"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.19,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lying in her lap while she \Npetted you made me env—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:48.43,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I mean, made you seem like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:50.10,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I am not a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:49.51,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.85,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I am a free, obedient Dragon who \Ngives her all for her mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:58.80,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thus our excursion to the \Nland of the demons ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.10,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,and we finally began our trip home...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.87,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,But our family gained \Nyet another new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:09.00,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Seems like things are about to get hectic...
